Description: SpatialSocialMedia allows plotting social media data over geographic grids using R base map library and the GADM database, a free spatial database of the location of the worldâ€™s administrative areas or boundaries. Network plots are generated using the capabilities of igraph, network, ggplot, ggplot2 (curved edges), or ggraph.
